Acceptance Criteria:
- createProject(title: String!, scriptType: ProjectType!) mutation creates a row in script.projects; returns { id title scriptType createdAt }
- projects(orgId: ID!, includeArchived: Boolean) query returns paginated list (first/after cursor) sorted by updatedAt desc; archived projects excluded unless includeArchived: true
- archiveProject(id: ID!) sets archived_at timestamp; project no longer appears in default list
- createScript(projectId: ID!, title: String!, scriptType: ScriptType!) creates row in script.scripts; returns { id title scriptType status }
- scripts(projectId: ID!) query returns all scripts in a project with { id title status updatedAt }
- script(id: ID!) query returns full script metadata including status, currentVersionId, and scene count
- All mutations enforce X-Org-ID header; cross-org data access returns 403
- Script GraphQL subgraph schema registered and supergraph recomposed successfully
